Articles.Content:
Hi all, Ever since I switched to KSP 1.7.3 and brought my many mods along with it, I've encountered an error from B9PartSwitch while loading the game that some errors have occurred. I'm not sure what they mean but it must be serious enough to tell me about it in this manner.

I think it's also affected some of my mods, because ive noticed that OPT is missing several parts, some of which are integral to my SSTOs and such. It says to see KSP's log for additional details but i'm not sure where to look in said logs, but I took some screenshots of what i'm talking about, if it helps at all: https://imgur.com/a/lHtfMxW

Just looking for some help, and to potentially restore the missing OPT parts. Thanks for your time.

Try reinstalling B9 part switch and/or bluedog mods, or update them to the latest versions.

Edited October 17, 2019 by spritefun
I was wrong at first lol
